          <title>Panthers stay active at NHL trade deadline by getting goalie Vitek Vanecek from the Sharks</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The defending Stanley Cup champion Florida Panthers continue to be active in the leadup to the NHL trade deadline. The Panthers acquired goaltender Vitek Vanecek on Wednesday from the San Jose Sharks for 25-year-old forward Patrick Giles, the teams announced.]]></description>
